---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Real Estate Agent Tingalpa Brisbane | Daniel Gierach"
  description="Daniel Gierach, real estate agent in Tingalpa Brisbane. Affordable inner-east suburb with great potential and growing buyer interest. Ray White Bulimba. Call 0412 523 821."
>

<script type="application/ld+json">{JSON.stringify({
  "@context": "https://schema.org",
  "@type": "WebPage",
  "name": "Real Estate Agent Tingalpa Brisbane",
  "description": "Daniel Gierach is a specialist real estate agent in Tingalpa Brisbane, serving Brisbane's eastern suburbs.",
  "url": "https://www.danielgierach.com/suburbs/tingalpa",
  "breadcrumb": {
    "@type": "BreadcrumbList",
    "itemListElement": [
      { "@type": "ListItem", "position": 1, "name": "Home", "item": "https://www.danielgierach.com" },
      { "@type": "ListItem", "position": 2, "name": "Tingalpa", "item": "https://www.danielgierach.com/suburbs/tingalpa" }
    ]
  }
})}</script>

<!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════
     SECTION 1: HERO
════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
<section style="background:#1c1917; color:#f2efe9; padding: 100px 24px 80px;">
  <div style="max-width:800px; margin:0 auto; text-align:center;">
    <p style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:0.75rem; font-weight:700; letter-spacing:0.15em; text-transform:uppercase; color:#c4912a; margin-bottom:1.25rem;">Tingalpa</p>
    <h1 style="font-family:var(--font-serif); font-size:clamp(2.4rem, 5vw, 4rem); font-weight:300; line-height:1.15; margin-bottom:1.5rem; color:#f2efe9;">
      Real Estate Agent<br/><em style="color:#f5d07a;">Tingalpa.</em>
    </h1>
    <p style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:1.05rem; font-weight:300; line-height:1.7; color:#c9c4bc; max-width:580px; margin:0 auto 2.5rem;">
      Specialist property sales in Tingalpa and Brisbane's eastern suburbs.
    </p>
    <div style="display:flex; gap:1rem; justify-content:center; flex-wrap:wrap;">
      <a href="/listings" class="btn-gold" style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:0.85rem; font-weight:700; letter-spacing:0.08em; text-transform:uppercase; background:#c4912a; color:#1c1917; padding:0.85rem 2rem; text-decoration:none; display:inline-block;">View Current Listings</a>
      <a href="/appraisal" class="btn-gold" style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:0.85rem; font-weight:700; letter-spacing:0.08em; text-transform:uppercase; background:#c4912a; color:#1c1917; padding:0.85rem 2rem; text-decoration:none; display:inline-block;">Request an Appraisal</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════
     SECTION 2: WHY THIS AREA
════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
<section style="background:var(--color-base, #f2efe9); padding:80px 24px;">
  <div style="max-width:800px; margin:0 auto;">
    <p style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:0.75rem; font-weight:700; letter-spacing:0.15em; text-transform:uppercase; color:#c4912a; margin-bottom:1rem;">Local Expertise</p>
    <h2 style="font-family:var(--font-serif); font-size:clamp(1.8rem, 3.5vw, 2.8rem); font-weight:300; line-height:1.2; color:#1c1917; margin-bottom:1.75rem;">Affordable entry with long-term potential.</h2>
    <p style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:1rem; font-weight:300; line-height:1.8; color:#4a4540; margin-bottom:1.25rem;">
      Tingalpa offers some of the best value in Brisbane's broader inner east. Larger blocks, good connectivity and improving infrastructure have attracted a growing number of first-home buyers and investors looking for yield and growth.
    </p>
    <p style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:1rem; font-weight:300; line-height:1.8; color:#4a4540; margin-bottom:1.25rem;">
      I understand the buyer profile active in Tingalpa and how to position properties to appeal to them. Whether you are selling a family home or an investment property, I will build a campaign that finds the right buyer at the right price.
    </p>
    <p style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:1rem; font-weight:300; line-height:1.8; color:#4a4540; margin-bottom:1.25rem;">
      Tingalpa Creek runs through the suburb's green edge, providing a natural amenity that buyers from denser suburbs notice and appreciate. The suburb's relative affordability compared with Cannon Hill and Murarrie makes it an attractive entry point for first-home buyers and investors who have been priced out of the inner-east ring. Industrial uses near the Gateway Motorway have historically kept values lower, but residential pockets away from that boundary have seen steady capital growth as buyers look further east. Infrastructure upgrades along the Gateway corridor continue to improve connectivity and have strengthened the suburb's investment case.
    </p>
    <div style="display:flex; gap:1.5rem; flex-wrap:wrap;">
      <div style="flex:1; min-width:200px; background:#fff; padding:1.75rem; border-left:3px solid #c4912a;">
        <p style="font-family:var(--font-serif); font-size:1.1rem; font-weight:400; color:#1c1917; margin-bottom:0.4rem;">Tingalpa Specialist</p>
        <p style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:0.85rem; font-weight:300; color:#6b6560;">Eastern Brisbane</p>
      </div>
      <div style="flex:1; min-width:200px; background:#fff; padding:1.75rem; border-left:3px solid #c4912a;">
        <p style="font-family:var(--font-serif); font-size:1.1rem; font-weight:400; color:#1c1917; margin-bottom:0.4rem;">Growth Potential</p>
        <p style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:0.85rem; font-weight:300; color:#6b6560;">Strong investor interest</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <p style="font-size:0.82rem;color:#78716c;margin-top:2rem;">Also selling in: <a href="/suburbs/murarrie" style="color:#c4912a;">Murarrie</a>, <a href="/suburbs/cannon-hill" style="color:#c4912a;">Cannon Hill</a>, <a href="/suburbs/hemmant" style="color:#c4912a;">Hemmant</a>.</p>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════
     SECTION 3: SUBURBS SERVED
════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
<section style="background:#fff; padding:80px 24px;">
  <div style="max-width:900px; margin:0 auto;">
    <p style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:0.75rem; font-weight:700; letter-spacing:0.15em; text-transform:uppercase; color:#c4912a; margin-bottom:1rem;">Areas Covered</p>
    <h2 style="font-family:var(--font-serif); font-size:clamp(1.8rem, 3.5vw, 2.8rem); font-weight:300; line-height:1.2; color:#1c1917; margin-bottom:2.5rem;">Suburbs I specialise in.</h2>
    <div style="display:grid; grid-template-columns:repeat(3, 1fr); gap:1.25rem;">
      <div style="background:var(--color-base, #f2efe9); padding:1.75rem;">
        <p style="font-family:var(--font-serif); font-size:1.15rem; font-weight:400; color:#1c1917; margin-bottom:0.5rem;">Tingalpa</p>
        <p style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:0.85rem; font-weight:300; color:#6b6560; line-height:1.6;">Affordable entry into Brisbane's inner east</p>
      </div>
      <div style="background:var(--color-base, #f2efe9); padding:1.75rem;">
        <p style="font-family:var(--font-serif); font-size:1.15rem; font-weight:400; color:#1c1917; margin-bottom:0.5rem;">Murarrie</p>
        <p style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:0.85rem; font-weight:300; color:#6b6560; line-height:1.6;">Emerging suburb with riverside access and growth potential</p>
      </div>
      <div style="background:var(--color-base, #f2efe9); padding:1.75rem;">
        <p style="font-family:var(--font-serif); font-size:1.15rem; font-weight:400; color:#1c1917; margin-bottom:0.5rem;">Cannon Hill</p>
        <p style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:0.85rem; font-weight:300; color:#6b6560; line-height:1.6;">Quiet streets and a strong sense of community</p>
      </div>
      <div style="background:var(--color-base, #f2efe9); padding:1.75rem;">
        <p style="font-family:var(--font-serif); font-size:1.15rem; font-weight:400; color:#1c1917; margin-bottom:0.5rem;">Carina</p>
        <p style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:0.85rem; font-weight:300; color:#6b6560; line-height:1.6;">Family-friendly suburb with quiet streets and great value</p>
      </div>
      <div style="background:var(--color-base, #f2efe9); padding:1.75rem;">
        <p style="font-family:var(--font-serif); font-size:1.15rem; font-weight:400; color:#1c1917; margin-bottom:0.5rem;">Wynnum</p>
        <p style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:0.85rem; font-weight:300; color:#6b6560; line-height:1.6;">Bayside lifestyle with strong community character</p>
      </div>
      <div style="background:var(--color-base, #f2efe9); padding:1.75rem;">
        <p style="font-family:var(--font-serif); font-size:1.15rem; font-weight:400; color:#1c1917; margin-bottom:0.5rem;">Hemmant</p>
        <p style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:0.85rem; font-weight:300; color:#6b6560; line-height:1.6;">Riverside suburb with a relaxed lifestyle feel</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════
     SECTION 4: HOW I CAN HELP YOU SELL
════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
<section style="background:var(--color-base, #f2efe9); padding:80px 24px;">
  <div style="max-width:800px; margin:0 auto;">
    <p style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:0.75rem; font-weight:700; letter-spacing:0.15em; text-transform:uppercase; color:#c4912a; margin-bottom:1rem;">Selling in Tingalpa</p>
    <h2 style="font-family:var(--font-serif); font-size:clamp(1.8rem, 3.5vw, 2.8rem); font-weight:300; line-height:1.2; color:#1c1917; margin-bottom:3rem;">What selling with Daniel looks like.</h2>
    <div style="display:flex; flex-direction:column; gap:2.5rem; margin-bottom:3rem;">
      <div style="display:flex; gap:2rem; align-items:flex-start;">
        <span style="font-family:var(--font-serif); font-size:2.5rem; font-weight:300; color:#c4912a; line-height:1; flex-shrink:0; width:2.5rem;">1</span>
        <div>
          <p style="font-family:var(--font-serif); font-size:1.2rem; font-style:italic; font-weight:400; color:#1c1917; margin-bottom:0.5rem;">Free appraisal</p>
          <p style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:0.9rem; font-weight:300; line-height:1.7; color:#6b6560;">I'll walk you through what your property is worth and what buyers are currently paying in your area.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div style="display:flex; gap:2rem; align-items:flex-start;">
        <span style="font-family:var(--font-serif); font-size:2.5rem; font-weight:300; color:#c4912a; line-height:1; flex-shrink:0; width:2.5rem;">2</span>
        <div>
          <p style="font-family:var(--font-serif); font-size:1.2rem; font-style:italic; font-weight:400; color:#1c1917; margin-bottom:0.5rem;">Tailored campaign</p>
          <p style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:0.9rem; font-weight:300; line-height:1.7; color:#6b6560;">Every property is different. I build a strategy around your home, your timeline and your buyer profile.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div style="display:flex; gap:2rem; align-items:flex-start;">
        <span style="font-family:var(--font-serif); font-size:2.5rem; font-weight:300; color:#c4912a; line-height:1; flex-shrink:0; width:2.5rem;">3</span>
        <div>
          <p style="font-family:var(--font-serif); font-size:1.2rem; font-style:italic; font-weight:400; color:#1c1917; margin-bottom:0.5rem;">Managed negotiation</p>
          <p style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:0.9rem; font-weight:300; line-height:1.7; color:#6b6560;">I manage every offer with commercial discipline to protect your final result.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <a href="/appraisal" style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:0.85rem; font-weight:700; letter-spacing:0.08em; text-transform:uppercase; background:#c4912a; color:#1c1917; padding:0.85rem 2rem; text-decoration:none; display:inline-block;">Request a Free Appraisal</a>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════
     SECTION 5: CTA STRIP
════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
<section style="background:#1c1917; color:#f2efe9; padding:80px 24px; text-align:center;">
  <div style="max-width:700px; margin:0 auto;">
    <h2 style="font-family:var(--font-serif); font-size:clamp(1.8rem, 3.5vw, 2.8rem); font-weight:300; line-height:1.2; color:#f2efe9; margin-bottom:1.25rem;">Thinking of selling in Tingalpa?</h2>
    <p style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:1rem; font-weight:300; line-height:1.75; color:#c9c4bc; margin-bottom:2rem;">Call me directly for a no-obligation conversation about your property and what it could achieve in today's market.</p>
    <p style="margin-bottom:2.5rem;">
      <a href="tel:+61412523821" style="font-family:var(--font-serif); font-size:2rem; font-weight:300; color:#f5d07a; text-decoration:none; letter-spacing:0.02em;">0412 523 821</a>
    </p>
    <div style="display:flex; gap:1rem; justify-content:center; flex-wrap:wrap;">
      <a href="/contact" style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:0.85rem; font-weight:700; letter-spacing:0.08em; text-transform:uppercase; background:transparent; color:#f2efe9; padding:0.85rem 2rem; text-decoration:none; display:inline-block; border:1px solid #c4912a;">Send a Message</a>
      <a href="/appraisal" style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:0.85rem; font-weight:700; letter-spacing:0.08em; text-transform:uppercase; background:#c4912a; color:#1c1917; padding:0.85rem 2rem; text-decoration:none; display:inline-block;">Request an Appraisal</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    section div[style*="grid-template-columns:repeat(3"] {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr) !important;
    }
  }
  @media (max-width: 480px) {
    section div[style*="grid-template-columns:repeat(3"] {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr !important;
    }
  }
</style>

</Layout>
